CERTIFICATE OF TAX, FEE OR ASSESSMENT DUE RENEWAL
(Pursuant to NRS 481.081)
THE STATE OF NEVADA, DEPARTMENT OF MOTOR VEHICLES, hereinafter referred to as
Department, hereby certifies that
ROBERT ALLEN SEILING
Is liable to the State of Nevada for amounts due from and required to be paid under the provisions of
Chapter(s) 353C, 481 of the Nevada Revised Statutes, in the amount of $250.00 plus interest at the rate of
1% per month from 08/04/2011 and any accumulating fines, penalties and interest which may be assessed
for additional violations until paid in full. The address of Robert Allen Seiling as it appears on the records
of the Department is:
3850 S VERDE AVE, PAHRUMP, NV 89048
And that the Department has complied with all provisions of Chapter(s) 353C, 481 of the Nevada Revised
Statutes, when applicable, in the determination of the amounts required to be paid.
IN WITNESS THEREOF, the Department has caused this Certificate to be executed.
